sentences: Judith Wessendorf (born 20 November 1992 in Berlin), better known under the stage name Juju, is a German rapper of German and Moroccan descent.
In 2010, she met Nura for the first time.
Their first song was Deine Mutter and their most successful Von Party zu Party (which reached 30 million views on Youtube two years later) and Bongzimmer.
In 2018, Nura and Juju separated and began their solo careers.
Juju reached the top of the German single charts with the singles "Melodien" (with Capital Bra), "Vermissen" (with Henning May) and "Kein Wort" (with Loredana).
